    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Does your child love all things space and superheroes? This Kidplokio Galaxy Sword and Cinch Bag Bundle set is a great gift idea this holiday season! The space sword toy features flashing colorful lights and fantastic sound effects, and the superhero-themed cinch bag comes with an easy-to-use drawstring cinch closure for on-the-go fun.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Kidplokio 2pc Space Gift Bundle Toy Sword and Superhero Cinch Bag (2 Colors)</h2>\n  <p>Does your child love all things space and superheroes? This Kidplokio Galaxy Sword and Cinch Bag Bundle set is a great gift idea this holiday season! The space sword toy features flashing colorful lights and fantastic sound effects, and the superhero-themed cinch bag comes with an easy-to-use drawstring cinch closure for on-the-go fun.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>SWORD TOY AND BACKPACK BUNDLE - Kidplokio Galaxy Sword and Backpack bundle comes with a cool light-up space sword and a superhero-themed cinch bag for boys; Sword fits inside a travel bag for on-the-go adventures</li>\n    <li><strong>AWESOME LIGHTS AND SOUNDS:</strong> Featuring stunning LED Lights that illuminate in vibrant colors when the grip trigger is engaged, this Galaxy Space Sword toy has an array of sounds and colorful light effects; this toy sword is ready for action with batteries included and no assembly required</li>\n    <li>LARGE CAPACITY BAG - Drawstring tote bag measures 18” and can easily hold children’s school supplies and sporting gear. Kids can securely carry their binders, notebooks, school books, and water bottles to and from school, sports practice, and play dates</li>\n    <li>DURABLE MATERIAL - Cinch backpacks are made of durable, water-resistant polyester to protect your child’s back-to-school materials and supplies even in inclement weather; Sword toy is made of plastic that can be easily wiped down and air-dried in between uses to keep it clean</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - 2pc bundle gift set (space sword and cinch bag); Colors:</strong> assorted; Recommended age: 3+ years; No assembly required (space sword); Batteries included</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/22368/space_sword_var.jpg\" alt=\"Does your child love all things space and superheroes\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KPL2PCSS</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Suit up with this futuristic space sword toy that comes with awesome LED lights and captivating sounds, making playtime even more fun and realistic for kids! They’ll be kept busy for hours conjuring up space rescue missions and alien battle scenarios with this futuristic space sword toy by their side. Lightweight and easy to hold, kids won’t have any problem wielding their new favorite sword.</p>\n  <p>Each drawstring tote bag measures 18” by 13” and can easily hold your child’s school supplies and sporting gear like binders, school books, notebooks, accessories, and a water bottle. The bag features an easy-to-use cinch closure to ensure supplies stay secured in the bag when not in use.</p>\n  <p>The adjustable cinch strap design provides customizable comfort that will fit most kids. The bag itself is made of durable water-resistant polyester to protect your child’s school materials and supplies rain or shine.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
